  "title": "Aerospace Technician @ Seletar | Up $3.2K | 1 year contract",
  "description": "<p>We're hiring a hands-on Technical Aircraft Specialist to join a high-performing team and contribute directly to production quality, process improvement, and new product launches.<br /></p><p><strong>🔑 Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide day-to-day technical support to production, ensuring optimal product performance and quality.</p></li><li><p>Manage product definition and evolution, working closely with IPT (Integrated Product Team).</p></li><li><p>Lead root cause analysis and implement quality improvement activities (8D, FTQP).</p></li><li><p>Coordinate new product introductions and support customer return investigations.</p></li><li><p>Drive continuous improvement initiatives (Kaizen) and maintain key KPIs (R1, FPY).</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with Design Authority and cross-functional teams across departments.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>🎁 Perks & Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><p>💼 Contract Type: 1 year contract, with possibility of conversion to permanent based on performance</p></li><li><p>💰 Completion Bonus</p></li><li><p>⏰ Working Hours: Monday – Friday, 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>✅ Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>NITEC / Higher NITEC / Diploma in Engineering</p></li><li><p>1–5 years of relevant hands-on experience in a manufacturing or technical support environment</p></li><li><p>Prefer applicant who has experience working in aviation industry<br /></p></li></ul><p>If you’re ready to make an impact and grow in a fast-paced, quality-driven environment — we want to hear from you!</p><p><strong>Email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:deborah@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">deborah@crew.sg</a></p><p>Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)</p><p>Crew by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd | EA License: 24C2435</p>",
